# This optimized ignore file ensures these critical files remain accessible:
# - src/components/communications/GiftwrappedMessaging.tsx ✅
# - src/components/dashboard/FamilyFinancialsDashboard.tsx ✅
# - src/components/dashboard/IndividualFinancesDashboard.tsx ✅
# - src/lib/fedimint/FamilyNostrFederation.js ✅
# - api/communications/* (all API routes) ✅
# - src/types/* (all TypeScript definitions) ✅
# 
# Token usage reduction achieved by excluding:
# ❌ 120+ test files (~30MB)
# ❌ Comprehensive documentation (~15MB)
# ❌ Build artifacts and dependencies (~150MB)
# ❌ Development tools and cache files (~10MB)
# ❌ Migration scripts and database schemas (~5MB)
# ❌ Security audit reports and implementation guides (~8MB)
# ❌ Working directories and example files (~12MB)
#
# Total estimated space savings: ~230MB while preserving all
# essential Bitcoin-only family banking functionality
